sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor EventBridge as EventBridge (Scheduler)
    participant Lambda as WeeklyJobLambda
    participant DB as Firebase (Firestore)
    participant Places as GooglePlacesAPI
    participant APNs as APNs
    participant Email as EmailService

    Note over EventBridge,Email: UC-008 Weekly Scheduled Job - select spot and create invites

    EventBridge->>Lambda: trigger(cron) Thursday 08:00
    activate Lambda

    Lambda->>DB: query all Cities where isActive == true
    DB-->>Lambda: [City...]

    loop for each active City
        Lambda->>DB: read VenueExclusionList(city, last 4 weekIds)
        DB-->>Lambda: excludedVenueIds[]

        Lambda->>Places: nearbySearch(city, type=bar/cafe/restaurant)
        alt Places API success
            Places-->>Lambda: candidateVenues[]

            Note over Lambda: Curate - rating >= 4.0,<br/>reviewCount >= 50,<br/>open weekdays,<br/>NOT in excludedVenueIds

            alt at least one venue passes curation
                Lambda->>Lambda: select spot (highest ranked eligible)
                Lambda->>DB: write WeeklySpot(city, weekId, venue...)
                Lambda->>DB: update VenueExclusionList(city, weekId, +venueId)

                Lambda->>DB: query Users where selectedCity == city
                DB-->>Lambda: [User...]

                Note over Lambda: Create Invite records for all users in this city

                loop for each User in city
                    Lambda->>DB: write Invite(userId, weekId, venueId, city, status=INVITED)
                end

                Lambda->>DB: read all PushToken(platform=IOS, isValid=true) for users in city
                DB-->>Lambda: [deviceToken...]

                loop for each valid device token
                    Lambda->>APNs: push(deviceToken, spot payload)
                    alt token rejected (410 / BadDeviceToken)
                        APNs-->>Lambda: error stale token
                        Lambda->>DB: mark PushToken.isValid = false
                    else delivered
                        APNs-->>Lambda: 200 OK
                        Lambda->>DB: update PushToken.lastUsedAt
                    end
                end

                Lambda->>DB: read all EmailAddress(isVerified=true) for users in city
                DB-->>Lambda: [email...]

                loop for each verified email
                    Lambda->>Email: send(email, spot details + RSVP link)
                    Email-->>Lambda: queued
                end

            else no eligible venue (all filtered/excluded)
                Note over Lambda: Failure branch - skip city this week
                Lambda->>DB: log warning(city, weekId, "no eligible venue")
            end

        else Places API failure / quota
            Places-->>Lambda: error
            Note over Lambda: Failure branch - skip city, retry next run
            Lambda->>DB: log error(city, weekId, places error)
        end
    end

    Lambda-->>EventBridge: complete (per-city status summary)
    deactivate Lambda
